<div class="NavHead" style="border-bottom:1px solid #aaa; background:transparent;"><a href="/wiki/Issues_in_anarchism" title="Issues in anarchism">Issues</a></div>
<div class="NavContent" style="padding:0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align:center;"><a href="/wiki/Anarchism_and_anarcho-capitalism" title="Anarchism and anarcho-capitalism">Anarcho-capitalism</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anarchism_and_animal_rights" title="Anarchism and animal rights">Animal rights</a><br />
